<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8145937>
    dc:description "Рис. 1–7. Новые ΑΛя фауны России и маΛоизвестные виΑы жуков-ΑоΛгоносиков. 1–3 – Cionus rossicus: 1 – самец, 2 – эΑеагус, 3 – самка; 4 – Cionus gebleri; 5 – Mecinus janthiniformis; 6 – Smicronyx robustus; 7 – Smicronyx albopictus. Figs 1–7. New to the fauna of Russia and little known species of weevils. 1–3 – Cionus rossicus: 1 – male, 2 – aedeagus,3 – female;4 – Cionus gebleri; 5 – Mecinus janthiniformis; 6 – Smicronyx robustus; 7 – Smicronyx albopictus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8145937/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

